	* character.h (STRING_CHAR_ADVANCE_UTF8): Sanitize the code.
	(STRING_CHAR_ADVANCE_UTF16): Likewise.

	* font.c (mfont__init): Initialize buf to NULL.
	(mfont__id): Likewise.

	* font-ft.c (ft_encapsulate): Use MDEBUG_PRINT1 instead of
	MDEBUG_DUMP.
