	(mdatabase__init): Initialize mdatabase__load_charset_func and
	Mcharset.  Don't set mdatabase__finder and mdatabase__loader.
	(mdatabase__save): Use fwrite, not mconv_encode_stream.
	(Mcharset): Declare it here.

