	(DEVICE_DELTA): Return 26.6 fixed point value.
	(adjust_anchor): Likewise.
	(mfont__ft_drive_otf): Use get_glyph_metric.

	* font-flt.c (mfont__flt_run): Pay attention to padding on
	printing debug info.

